From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: BBC News 28 Feb 2001 2400 GMT [edited

United Kingdom
----------------------
The first case of FMD has been confirmed in Northern Ireland. 25 other
outbreaks are now confirmed in England & Scotland.
France
----------
A total of 30 000 sheep that have been in contact with British sheep are to
be slaughtered.
