[For a map of the location of the outbreaks across the UK, please see:
<http://news.bbc.co.uk/hi/english/uk/newsid_1194000/1194733.stm>
This devastating situation affects not only animals, but the livelihood of
farmers and of a nation. The helplessness of seeing your animals, your very
livelihood, slaughtered and no way to pay the bills and support a family is
devastating to the farmers; even to the nation as they continue to face the
crisis of FMD, higher food prices and, potentially, food shortages within
the country. - Mod.TG
